<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Daftar Gagal</title>

<style>
*{
  margin:0;
  padding:0;
  box-sizing:border-box;
  font-family:'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
}

body{
  height:100vh;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  align-items:center;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f2027,#203a43,#2c5364);
  color:#fff;
}

.container{
  text-align:center;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  padding:50px 40px;
  border-radius:20px;
  backdrop-filter:blur(15px);
  box-shadow:0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  max-width:500px;
  width:90%;
  animation:fadeIn 0.8s ease;
}

.icon{
  font-size:80px;
  margin-bottom:20px;
  animation:shake 0.6s ease;
}

h1{
  font-size:32px;
  margin-bottom:15px;
  letter-spacing:1px;
}

p{
  font-size:16px;
  opacity:0.9;
  margin-bottom:30px;
  line-height:1.6;
}

.btn{
  display:inline-block;
  padding:14px 28px;
  border-radius:30px;
  text-decoration:none;
  font-weight:bold;
  background:#ff4b5c;
  color:white;
  transition:0.3s;
  box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(255,75,92,0.4);
}

.btn:hover{
  transform:translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow:0 12px 25px rgba(255,75,92,0.6);
}

.note{
  margin-top:20px;
  font-size:13px;
  opacity:0.7;
}

@keyframes fadeIn{
  from{opacity:0; transform:translateY(20px);}
  to{opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);}
}

@keyframes shake{
  0%{transform:translateX(0);}
  25%{transform:translateX(-8px);}
  50%{transform:translateX(8px);}
  75%{transform:translateX(-5px);}
  100%{transform:translateX(0);}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">
  <div class="icon">❌</div>
  <h1>Pendaftaran Gagal</h1>
  <p>
    Data yang kamu masukkan kosong, tidak valid atau sudah terdaftar.<br>
    Pastikan semua field terisi dengan benar dan belum pernah digunakan.
  </p>

  <a href="/#register" class="btn">Coba Daftar Lagi</a>

  <div class="note">
    Jika masalah berlanjut, hubungi admin sistem.
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
